        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> Interact</p>\n<p>Cultivated by mashing and fermenting toxic weeds found in lonely graveyards, fearweed is a greenish paste magically infused with psychic horror. The @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened} condition from fearweed can't be removed while the poison lasts.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"30\" data-pf2-traits=\"contact,divine,poison\" data-pf2-label=\"Fearweed DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span></p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 minute</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong>[[/r {7d6}[poison]]]{7d6 poison damage} and frightened 1 (1 minute)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong>[[/r {8d6}[poison]]]{8d6 poison damage} and frightened 2 (1 minute)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> [[/r {9d6}[poison]]]{9d6 poison damage} and frightened 3 (1 minute)</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of 4th-level <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Fear]{Fear}</em>.</p>"
